high_descs: Take a step forward then turn left and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the garbage.
Pick up the soap dispenser in the garbage.
Turn right at the second cabinet to your left and then walk to the wall in front of you then turn right to face the toilet.
Put the soap dispenser on the back of the toilet near the handle.
Turn right and walk to the small end table.
Pick up the soap dispenser near the tissues on top of the table.
Walk back to where you put the first soap dispenser.
Put the soap dispenser to the left of the first on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two soap dispensers on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the trash can on the right.
Pick up the lotion from the trash can.
Carry the lotion and turn right.  Then right again and face the toilet on the right side.
Place the lotion on the toilet tank.
Turn to the right and locate the tall dresser.
Pick up the lotion bottle from the top of the dresser.
Hold the lotion and turn around. Face the toilet on the right side.
Place the lotion on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two lotion bottles to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the door, turn right, go to the garbage can.
Pick up the bottle of lotion that is in the garbage can.
Turn to the right, go to the sink and hang a right, go to the wall, hang a right and go to the toilet.
Put the lotion on the back of the toilet.
Turn to the right, go to the counter across the room where the box of tissues is.
Pick up the bottle of lotion that is behind the box of tissues.
Turn around, head back to the toilet across the room.
Put the bottle of lotion on the back of the toilet next to the other bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of lotion on the back of the toilet.
